data.description: Come take a look at this well-kept residence nestled in the desirable Madera Highlands Village community in Sahuarita. This immaculately kept home is perfect for families seeking a serene neighborhood to raise their families and enjoy community activities. With three spacious bedrooms, two full bathrooms, and oversized two car garage, there's plenty of room to grow.  As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the tile flooring that flows seamlessly throughout the entire home. The open floorplan and vaulted ceilings create an airy atmosphere, perfect for entertaining and everyday living. The heart of the home is the stylish kitchen, which boasts mid-tone cabinetry, a center island, stainless appliances, and a large pantry to fulfill all of your culinary needs.  The thoughtful split bedroom arrangement provides privacy for every family member, with the primary suite located in the back of the home and two children's rooms at the front. The generously-sized lot offers an amazing aluminum covered gazebo, creating an inviting outdoor living space for you to enjoy year-round.  Madera Highlands is a family-oriented community that provides residents with an array of amenities, including parks, a basketball court, a tennis court and a swimming pool. This idyllic neighborhood is the perfect setting for creating lasting memories with your loved ones.
